12.) What about the concerns of #BTC getting hacked?

#BTC itself hasn't been hacked.

"Not your keys, not your crypto."

If you trust someone else with your assets, then there is always a risk it can be stolen.

That applies in all asset classes [Stocks/Metals/etc].
